Package org.turbogwt.ext.gwtp.databind.client

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DatabindUiHandlers
    Use this interface on classes that implement the controls required by a DatabindView to communicate back with its PresenterWidget.
    DatabindView<H extends DatabindUiHandlers>
    The interface for view classes that handles all the UI-related code for a Presenter supporting Databind.
    PopupDatabindView<H extends DatabindUiHandlers>
    The interface for View classes that is meant to be displayed as a popup supporting Databind.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatabindViewImpl<H extends DatabindUiHandlers>
    Base class for a DatabindView.
    PopupDatabindViewImpl<H extends DatabindUiHandlers>
    Base class for a PopupDatabindView.
